102
00:04:35,971 --> 00:04:37,928
For those who think light is more important,

103
00:04:37,952 --> 00:04:40,024
they tend to focus more on drawing accurately.

104
00:04:41,141 --> 00:04:42,993
So, these people tend to

105
00:04:43,587 --> 00:04:46,484
focus on the volume.

106
00:04:46,495 --> 00:04:47,516
Most of the time.

107
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:49,647
For those who put an emphasis on the texture,

108
00:04:49,672 --> 00:04:51,827
they usually focus more on the Pen Touch,

109
00:04:52,285 --> 00:04:57,119
and unique touches and description of textures.

110
00:04:57,207 --> 00:04:59,330
They focus more on those things

111
00:04:59,691 --> 00:05:01,691
