240
00:11:23,669 --> 00:11:27,453
If this stick goes down,

241
00:11:27,477 --> 00:11:28,490
then it will become different.

242
00:11:29,643 --> 00:11:32,297
If this stick goes down,

243
00:11:32,322 --> 00:11:35,478
